The '''Kasi''' ({{lang-ps|کاسي}}) or '''Kansi''' ({{lang-ps|کانسي}}) is a [[Pashtuns|Pashtun]] tribe from the [[Sarbani]] tribal confederacy, primarily found in [[Balochistan, Pakistan]] and in [[Loy Kandahar]], [[Afghanistan]]. 

